Items.mt: I was passing by here for other purposes, but I heard about you accidentally, so I came here half-heartedly, but I didn't expect you were really hiding here!

Items.r: 原本因为其他目的才经过这里，结果无意间听到你的消息，便半信半疑地来了，没想到你还真躲在这！
